{"tid":2488634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗議美國派特使訪台 支那決定在領海邊連2波實彈軍演","createTime":"2021-04-14T11:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T11:20:57.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8eec8b88f821a0dd5ba75acdc563da4776df53","tid":2488634,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">【美特使訪台】中國挑釁「加碼」 連2波實彈軍演逼臨台海</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仇佩芬<br />\n2021年4月14日 週三 下午5:39&middot;2 分鐘 (閱讀時間)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">美國總統拜登派遣政壇密友前參議員陶德（Chris Dodd）率團訪台之際，中國海事局發布海上實彈軍演消息，將於15日至20日於廣東沿海南澎列島附近海域進行實彈射擊演習。演習區域雖然在廣東近海，範圍並不算大，然而已相當接近台灣海峽南端，在美中台三方緊張關係升高之際，挑釁意味頗為明顯。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國海事局14日發布航行警告，將自15日至20日於南海、南澎列島附近海域進行實彈射擊演習，演習期間禁止船隻進入相關範圍。事實上，在此一區域的稍南區域，目前正在進行另一項實彈射擊演習，演習期間為13日至17日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/osqa1NjCQ.wVoM.QXEzijA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4zNjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/rK347osj71ErbyJXiK78mg--~B/aD02NjY7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/no/upmedia.mg.tw/a0eeb95d540942a9cbde57a65c42debb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fosqa1NjCQ.wVoM.QXEzijA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4zNjtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrK347osj71ErbyJXiK78mg--~B%2FaD02NjY7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fno%2Fupmedia.mg.tw%2Fa0eeb95d540942a9cbde57a65c42debb&h=a61473bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3WTYJXRecnknaAQQft7RAw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4zNjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/HkzuftqpSD.bIEGAT7EGoA--~B/aD02NjY7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/no/upmedia.mg.tw/6afeaa9b2ce8ffcdf818d1901b0836df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3WTYJXRecnknaAQQft7RAw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4zNjtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHkzuftqpSD.bIEGAT7EGoA--~B%2FaD02NjY7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fno%2Fupmedia.mg.tw%2F6afeaa9b2ce8ffcdf818d1901b0836df&h=489e870d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">解放軍機擾台加碼2軍演 時機地點極敏感</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n近來解放軍機頻繁侵擾台灣，不但超過10天接連派軍機執行擾台任務，12日擾台軍機架次更高達25架，創下單日最多紀錄。美國國務院及白宮接連向中國喊話，要求中國停止威嚇台灣的行為。<br />\n<br />\n而在美國國務院發布新版《對台交往準則》，並派遣陶德擔任拜登個人特使訪問台灣後，中國接連在廣東沿海舉行2波實彈演習，地點緊鄰敏感的台灣海峽南端，其中15日展開的演習在時間上更緊扣陶德訪團抵台時間，在美中台三方關係緊張之際，更有展現挑釁態度的意味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tXzqmWKpRnLB5HSI2xYuFA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4zNjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/GtHZxf2212aXvxoJylc1rg--~B/aD02NjY7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/no/upmedia.mg.tw/07a4088f06809e822501fcd897457ec5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtXzqmWKpRnLB5HSI2xYuFA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4zNjtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGtHZxf2212aXvxoJylc1rg--~B%2FaD02NjY7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fno%2Fupmedia.mg.tw%2F07a4088f06809e822501fcd897457ec5&h=c67d5e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國務院發布新版《對台交往準則》後，派遣拜登個人特使陶德14日訪台。（外交部提供）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">非官方訪台「只是幌子」 國台辦批美騙人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而針對美國接連公開表達挺台言行，中國也拉高反擊聲浪。除了中國外交部重申立場，要求美方謹守「一個中國」政策外，中國國台辦發言人馬曉光14日更在記者會上重申中方反對任何形式的台美官方交往，更痛批美國「所謂官方和非官方，只不過是他們騙人的幌子」，強調台美之間的任何接觸改變不了台灣是中國一部分的事實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E7%89%B9%E4%BD%BF%E8%A8%AA%E5%8F%B0-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81-%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC-%E9%80%A32%E6%B3%A2%E5%AF%A6%E5%BD%88%E8%BB%8D%E6%BC%94%E9%80%BC%E8%87%A8%E5%8F%B0%E6%B5%B7-093900697.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%2589%25B9%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258C%2591%25E9%2587%2581-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A2%25BC-%25E9%2580%25A32%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%25BD%2588%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BC%2594%25E9%2580%25BC%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25B5%25B7-093900697.html&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=60f630dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E7%89%B9%E4%BD%BF%E8%A8%AA%E5%8F%B0-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81-%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC-%E9%80%A32%E6%B3%A2%E5%AF%A6%E5%BD%88%E8%BB%8D%E6%BC%94%E9%80%BC%E8%87%A8%E5%8F%B0%E6%B5%B7-093900697.html</a>"},{"pid":"6b619ce2e6942d4a77f7b3bfa48667b24bd54780","tid":2488634,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FJixMojeAR_8Jy47pvxZ5A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/T2H82DBvmF0gqzJnuW8j0g--~B/aD01NDU7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/setn.com.tw/2db40422c242790bbb385223b0475153\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFJixMojeAR_8Jy47pvxZ5A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FT2H82DBvmF0gqzJnuW8j0g--~B%2FaD01NDU7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F2db40422c242790bbb385223b0475153&h=0f4aab8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國宣布在台灣海峽進行實彈演習（圖／翻攝自中國廣東海事局）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4XT2FY_Xt.tr07nl95Julw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNC40O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/7WzDkyZ0TVw5n8T4fI61iA--~B/aD01MTI7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/setn.com.tw/dc956b801ab61479c0dd2acb8b1102e8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4XT2FY_Xt.tr07nl95Julw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNC40O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7WzDkyZ0TVw5n8T4fI61iA--~B%2FaD01MTI7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fdc956b801ab61479c0dd2acb8b1102e8&h=b9ab623a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國實彈演習射擊範圍就在台灣海峽近澎湖縣範圍。（翻攝自GOOGLE地圖）"},{"pid":"de03739f8502a919b1f109f1d7fd846972ad8661","tid":2488634,"uid":41861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>演習區域雖然在廣東近海，範圍並不算大，然而已相當接近台灣海峽南端</blockquote> 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入都唔敢入"},{"pid":"4954b262b02ae4b437faf547efc1af7633b32e7a","tid":2488634,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:11:52.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報似乎搞錯位置"},{"pid":"14304a7b11d272e6bc9322a81c85667a2054673a","tid":2488634,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">好悶，係就快。</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c7d92c6d9e406f820906cf1642456edef69c1ca","tid":2488634,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:13:42.000Z","msg":"共匪怎麼不敢越過海峽中線？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18f7851540be5ae381ecf0858db8e496f051f83","tid":2488634,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7d92c6d9e406f820906cf1642456edef69c1ca","tid":2488634,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:13:42.000Z","msg":"共匪怎麼不敢越過海峽中線？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"行過去都唔敢, 仲話越過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07016ec57ed99d00dd5fe6d541e73481d753eaba","tid":2488634,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f18f78